creator: WeCon
descriptionHtml:
Enjoy chatting with people all over the world!

# Easy registration
- All you need is a nickname, age and your gender!

# Bookmark your friends
- Bookmark people who you enjoy chat with.
You can get back to them easily :)

# Variety types of chat messages
- Tired of just texting? Try sending them images, videos and audios~!

# Recently accessed users
- We show users who’ve accessed the app recently at the top. More likely to get a reply!

# Blocking inadequate users
- We filter users who’s been reported by other users, and we also monitor user’s nickname and profile images everyday to filter out users with abusive/obscene message/images.
- Help us make a clean chat community :)

# Wonderful UI
- Probably the most descent UI among all other random chatting apps.

# Frequent Updates
- We’ll update app frequently fixing bugs & adding new features!
- Always contact us through ‘Help Center’ for feature request~ :)

--------------------------------------

*** Disclaimer ***

"All Chat" lets users around the world communicate easily. Each individual users take full responsibility on the actions they take while using our app. We, "Wecon", are not responsible for illegal acts each individuals make, ignoring the warnings stated throughout the app use.

Enjoy chatting with people all over the world!

# Easy registration
- All you need is a nickname, age and your gender!

# Bookmark your friends
- Bookmark people who you enjoy chat with.
You can get back to them easily :)

# Variety types of chat messages
- Tired of just texting? Try sending them images, videos and audios~!

# Recently accessed users
- We show users who’ve accessed the app recently at the top. More likely to get a reply!

# Blocking inadequate users
- We filter users who’s been reported by other users, and we also monitor user’s nickname and profile images everyday to filter out users with abusive/obscene message/images.
- Help us make a clean chat community :)

# Wonderful UI
- Probably the most descent UI among all other random chatting apps.

# Frequent Updates
- We’ll update app frequently fixing bugs & adding new features!
- Always contact us through ‘Help Center’ for feature request~ :)

--------------------------------------

*** Disclaimer ***

"Random Chat" lets users around the world communicate easily. Each individual users take full responsibility on the actions they take while using our app. We, "Wecon", are not responsible for illegal acts each individuals make, ignoring the warnings stated throughout the app use.
